{
  "texts": [
    "Table 2: Content safety risk taxonomy for AEGIS2.0 dataset.",
    "Conversation labels from human annotators are standardized to one of Safe, Needs Caution or one of the risk categories listed here.",
    "of the official taxonomy.",
    "If a sample did not fit within either the taxonomy or the provided list, they were encouraged to freely write any hazard category they deemed appropriate.",
    "To obtain standardized labels for model training, we analyzed the distribution of samples across the newly identified fine-grained categories and retained only those with a sufficiently high number of occurrences."
  ]
}